            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "One of the best school, We didn't realise the value of the school till we have opted other school due to personal reasons. The school staffs are kind enough to make the kids learn with fun. They haven't pressurised kid at any point. They are capable enough to make every kid to perform on Sports day. Only thing they have to upgrade is their road facilities. Management is kind enough to talk with parents and it will not in most of the schools. This school might be the one of the few schools that builds good relationships with parents",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
