            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Hi.. Recently visited this school for enquiring about admission for KG & primary. Admission Co-ordinator gave clear cut information about the school and admission process. The co-ordinator was very friendly to the children and also cleared all our doubts patiently in detail. I was completely satisfied with the details that I gathered there. Ambience of the school was also too good. Thanks Anan! :)",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
