            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "The idea about the observatory session is cool. In the observatory session, parents can observe the children's activity in the class. We visited the Creative class,  the teacher made sure that every child was involved in the class and it was a clever move to use the shapes to create an animal drawing that helped children understand and draw easily. We are really glad about the teacher's thought process.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
